getAudioAttributesFromLastVibration().name: getAudioAttributesFromLastVibration()
getAudioAttributesFromLastVibration().documentation: Returns the {@link AudioAttributes} from the last vibration.

getEffectId().name: getEffectId()
getEffectId().documentation:
Returns the last vibration effect ID of a {@link VibrationEffect#Prebaked} (e.g. {@link VibrationEffect#EFFECT_CLICK}).

This field is non-zero only if a {@link VibrationEffect#Prebaked} was ever requested.

getMilliseconds().name: getMilliseconds()
getMilliseconds().documentation: Returns the last vibration duration in MS.

getPrimitiveEffects().name: getPrimitiveEffects()
getPrimitiveEffects().documentation: Returns the last list of {@link PrimitiveEffect}.

getPrimitiveSegmentsInPrimitiveEffects().name: getPrimitiveSegmentsInPrimitiveEffects()
getPrimitiveSegmentsInPrimitiveEffects().documentation: Returns the last list of {@link PrimitiveSegment} vibrations in {@link PrimitiveEffect}.

getRepeat().name: getRepeat()
getRepeat().documentation: Returns the last vibration repeat times.

getVibrationAttributesFromLastVibration(.name: getVibrationAttributesFromLastVibration()
getVibrationAttributesFromLastVibration(.documentation: Returns the {@link VibrationAttributes} from the last vibration.

getVibrationEffectSegments().name: getVibrationEffectSegments()
getVibrationEffectSegments().documentation: Returns the last list of {@link VibrationEffectSegment}.

isCancelled().name: isCancelled()
isCancelled().documentation: Returns true if the Vibrator has been cancelled.

isVibrating().name: isVibrating()
isVibrating().documentation:
Returns true if the Vibrator is currently vibrating as controlled by {@link
Vibrator#vibrate(long)}

setHasAmplitudeControl(boolean).name: setHasAmplitudeControl(boolean)
setHasAmplitudeControl(boolean).documentation: Controls the return value of {@link Vibrator#hasAmplitudeControl()} the default is false.

setHasVibrator(boolean).name: setHasVibrator(boolean)
setHasVibrator(boolean).documentation: Controls the return value of {@link Vibrator#hasVibrator()} the default is true.
